# Optional Documentation Folder

This folder is for any additional documentation you want to include with your project.

## Examples of What You Can Put Here:

- **features.md** - Detailed breakdown of features
- **design-notes.md** - Your design decisions and planning
- **testing-notes.md** - Manual testing results
- **screenshots/** - Folder for program screenshots
- **peer-review.md** - Peer review feedback notes
- **reflections.md** - Daily development reflections

## Note:

This folder is **optional**. If you don't need it, you can delete it or leave it empty.

The main documentation should be in your **README.md** at the root of the project.
